<ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">LABORATORY WATER USED FOR</ENAMEX> CULTURING AND <ENAMEX TYPE="PRODUCT">TEST DILUTION</ENAMEX>
<ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">WATER</ENAMEX>


4.4.1 The quality of <ENAMEX TYPE="SUBSTANCE">water</ENAMEX> used for test <ENAMEX TYPE="SUBSTANCE">organism culturing</ENAMEX> and
for dilution <ENAMEX TYPE="SUBSTANCE">water</ENAMEX> used in toxicity tests is extremely important.
<ENAMEX TYPE="SUBSTANCE">Water</ENAMEX> for these <NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">two</NUMEX> uses should come from the same <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">source</ENAMEX>. The
<ENAMEX TYPE="SUBSTANCE">dilution water</ENAMEX> used in effluent toxicity tests will depend in part
