discussed in <ENAMEX TYPE="LAW">Section 5</ENAMEX>, <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Facilities, Equipment</ENAMEX> and Supplies. Water
used for culturing and test dilution should be analyzed for toxic
