metal, should not exceed <NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">1</NUMEX> <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">mg</ENAMEX>/L each, and <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Cd</ENAMEX>, <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Hg</ENAMEX>, and <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Ag</ENAMEX>, expressed
as total <ENAMEX TYPE="SUBSTANCE">metal</ENAMEX>, should not exceed <NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">100</NUMEX> <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">ng</ENAMEX>/L each. Total
